Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:52.72,Ending - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}自分のやりかた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:55.85,Ending - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}きっと見つけなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:23:00.85,Ending - JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}ねじ曲がった性格で
