Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:35.29,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}这是第几回了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:36.78,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}如果刚到手就丢了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.78,0:22:39.46,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一定会一直重蹈覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:42.71,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}轻松而又简单的目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.71,0:22:45.71,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}这种东西是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:49.63,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}如果渴望自由的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:52.72,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}使用自己的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:55.85,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一定是找不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:23:00.85,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}以这扭曲的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:03.90,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}制定万无一失的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:08.15,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我将马上前往去迎接你的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:09.74,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}请等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.16,0:23:12.78,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}即使这是不可能的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:15.83,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}也会用尽想象力克服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.49,0:23:18.58,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}要是一不小心陷入僵局
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:21.88,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那时候便去随机应变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:25.09,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}本应是一无所有的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:28.38,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}却为此欢呼雀跃停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:30.63,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}这个世界将一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:34.01,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}属于我们的
